13:49.243 --> 13:50.910 align:middle line:84%
Now that I've laid
all that out for you,

13:50.910 --> 13:53.520 align:middle line:84%
take 10 minutes to think
about how an investor would

13:53.520 --> 13:55.606 align:middle line:90%
hear your pitch.

